      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-100 DM 1&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 1 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-1 body, which is a nimble general-purpose missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_BLASTFRAG warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

